flowchart LR
    U["上游 event payload"] --> C["AF 字段契约检查"]
    C -->|"字段名和语义一致"| N["标准化 AF event"]
    C -->|"语义错误"| B["错误数据进入 AF"]

    N --> E["Shopee/UC enrichment"]
    N --> R["Risk rules / features"]
    N --> L["Black / white / grey lists"]
    N --> V["IVlog / ES / NLA / DWH"]

    E --> OK["正确决策和排查上下文"]
    R --> OK
    L --> OK
    V --> OK

    B --> X1["查询失败或 IVlog 缺失"]
    B --> X2["名单误命中或漏命中"]
    B --> X3["规则特征错误"]
    B --> X4["历史证据和 replay 被污染"]

    M["例子：merchantUid"] -->|"只能是 merchant Shopee UID"| C
    S["例子：shopeeStatus"] -->|"只能是 Shopee account status enum"| C
